>For single press make sure you hold the button down long enough
-Display is automatically turned off after 70s of inactivity - Press X/Y once to wake it
1. Photo Mode Controls
Button:
A - Single press - capture photo in either AF/MF
A - Double press - Toggle live preview
B - Single Press - View last photo taken in gallery
B - Double press - Switch to settings mode
X - Double press - toggle AF <-> MF
Y - Double press - Shutdown
X/Y - Single Press - Wake the screen if it dims
2. Settings Mode Controls
X - Single press - Select previous setting
Y - Single press - Select next setting
X/Y - Double press - Modify selected setting
A - No Action
B - Double press - Return to photo mode
-Settings List:
ISO - value range - 50 ->800 
Brightness - 0.5 -> 1.5
Focus Mode - Toggle AF <-> MF
3. Gallery Mode (Photo Viewer)
A - Single press - Exit image viewer
X - Single press - Previous image
Y - Single press - Next image
